        <body>
            <p><persName role="author">Jacob Mendes de Sola</persName> writes<lb/> on the
                        <date>23<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">rd</hi></hi> of Iyar 1851
                    (5611)</date><lb/> to thank <persName>I. L.</persName> for having
                recommended<lb/> him to the community of <placeName>Richmond</placeName><lb/> to
                    <persName>Mr. J. A. Levy</persName> of that congregation<lb/> He, <persName
                    role="author">J</persName> the writer, was elected<lb/> Hazan and teacher.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">He asks <persName>I. L.</persName> to suggest text<lb/> books.</p>
            <p rend="indent(1)">There is mention also of<lb/>
                <persName>Mr. A. Hart</persName> of <placeName>Phila.</placeName> to whom<lb/> the
                writer sends greetings.</p>
        </body>
